Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.83,0:11:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a moral contest. If you read the\Nevening news, the world is engaged in an
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.16,0:11:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,endless of who's got the moral high\Nground.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.48,0:11:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's got the moral high ground? The\Nclash of civilizations is who's got the
