Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.20,0:13:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.\NSo we'll move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.68,0:13:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh this is lower mind. This is this kind\Nof thinking is what characterizes the
