Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.16,0:13:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,mind sees things not in terms of what\Ntheir cash is but their true value. It
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:14:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,sees potential. So higher mind is more\Ninto aesthetics. It's more intuitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.27,0:14:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's actually more intelligent and it\Nlooks to serve life. It looks to serve
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,life. Looks to serve life. when I was in\Npractice. My obligation in my view was
